node.text: There is something about pink 💓 icing that make cupcakes 🧁 look (and taste) sweeter ☺️ and prettier 🎀! Vanilla cupcakes by me and the little one 👧🏻 from the other day 💘 TGIF everyone! 😘 #tgif #cupcakes #cupcakesofinstagram #cupcakedecorating #prettyinpink #sweets #dessert #cake #stayhomestaysafe #circuitbreakersg #sgunited
@pcramerfun Pink just makes everything better right? 💕💕
@vinvola Hehe! Look forward to meeting up next time! 💕
Yumm!! N pretty , can’t wait to try your bakes 😜
Ah they look so nice!! 😍❤️ Enjoy

@makeupwithlouise Thanks Dear! Too much sugar in the icing tho 😝
@xav07sg Thank you!! Means so much coming from a top chef! 😁
